sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Utilisateur
    participant F as Angular Frontend
    participant AC as AuthController
    participant SS as Spring Security
    participant DB as Base de Donnees

    U->>F: Saisir email + mot de passe
    F->>AC: POST /api/auth/login
    AC->>SS: authenticate(credentials)
    SS->>DB: SELECT FROM utilisateur WHERE email=?
    DB-->>SS: Utilisateur trouve
    SS->>SS: Verifier BCrypt password
    SS-->>AC: Authentication validee
    AC->>AC: Generer JWT Token (24h)
    AC-->>F: 200 OK {token, role, user}
    F->>F: Stocker token localStorage
    F-->>U: Redirection Dashboard
